вҖў /browser: Manage local browser/CDP connection
вҖў /skills: Browse available skills
вҖў /packs: Manage packs (install, enable, disable, uninstall)
вҖў /reload-mcp: Reload MCP config and refresh MCP tools for this session
вҖў /resume: Show the latest interrupted-turn resume note
вҖў /approvals: Show current one-time, session, and persistent approvals
вҖў /revoke: Revoke a persistent approval by id
вҖў /yolo: Toggle session YOLO/open mode; hard safety blocks still apply
вҖў /cron: Manage scheduled tasks
вҖў /trust: Trust this workspace for proactive local work
вҖў /untrust: Revoke workspace trust
вҖў /workspace.trust.status: Show whether the current workspace is trusted
вҖў /doctor: Run a quick in-session health check
вҖў /workflow: Workflow operator commands (status, pause, resume, steer, trace, etc.)
